# Dropbox Integration Environment Variables

# Dropbox App Key (Client ID)
# Get this from https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
DROPBOX_APP_KEY=your_app_key_here

# Dropbox App Secret
# Get this from https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
DROPBOX_APP_SECRET=your_app_secret_here

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
# 2. Create a new app or select an existing one
# 3. Choose "Scoped access" as the API type
# 4. Select "Full Dropbox" or "App folder" access
# 5. Copy the App Key and App Secret
# 6. Add the OAuth2 redirect URI: http://localhost:3000/api/auth/dropbox/callback
# 7. Enable the following permissions in the Permissions tab:
#    - files.content.read
#    - files.content.write
#    - files.metadata.read
#    - files.metadata.write
#    - account_info.read
# 8. Submit the app for production use if needed
